{"id":"7c957296-28d8-44be-82c7-3bc41c4cab4c","title":"1551/06/21: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"9f9430fd-15b2-45a7-8653-9886190a7f0b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, June 28th, 1551.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"dceeaae5-d059-4404-8c6e-fe63b35173fe","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0538afda-854b-4b9d-a665-02dfbfd5fed8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"dd27934a-9c7e-4f70-9564-c2d663d4f66e","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":25,"value":"a440aebc-84a3-4f8b-ac32-37e632f7916d","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2f55f65c-b60f-4057-a81f-f739163231e1","type":"style/superscript","start":18,"end":19,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"875f4c89-0b63-4dfc-b41b-ca601fcdf2d3","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"d800c44d-6ce3-47e8-9dbf-5f4e0b77da96","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b21f1b46-653a-4c15-99f3-eaf02271a1c7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"0cd8864d-ab77-4fe0-9381-db15a63a0949","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"6c987066-ef11-4cf1-bab6-a680f89da986","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0b5408fb-d814-45fc-a86e-0dbfa6a1f5db","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"68f4c679-7116-4f12-a73f-18b6d2c12d63","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"d99bfbd4-497d-428f-aff9-51b4fc3e876b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0A week ago I received a load of Trebbiano, that is to say forty 4 (sic) flasks : I have given away some of it to several of my friends, and it is\u00A0considered to be the best of this [last] year\u0027s vintage\u00A0that has reached Rome. I thank thee for it: I have nothing more to add on the subject.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c817d7fe-3fe8-4f7a-a7a4-571a23921cf8","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1ce508b1-4c61-4b40-8375-8b380ba271df","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bb72d4a2-888a-4fec-8ee7-92470247ddb8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":23,"end":23,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"12f5dfcd-0be7-4a1c-812a-9e017bcc505d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":44,"end":52,"value":"0817adc9-541e-41f6-bc16-5dd3b78a6404","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"423c6dfe-f6f6-45c6-ad9e-60e05cb934c9","type":"style/italics","start":79,"end":81,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8b261e54-dad0-482e-b9e1-bcdf0fb50bbb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":93,"end":93,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c485dfc4-b0a2-4aee-8316-bf57ffa75023","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":119,"end":120,"value":"0817adc9-541e-41f6-bc16-5dd3b78a6404","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b23223fa-e913-4f26-bb8c-a9b5ce23d5b2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":136,"end":137,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"116c0e36-50b3-4ac9-a591-45b047d42a04","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":139,"end":145,"value":"4f58491e-e88a-45b1-88bc-95a081bf97a8","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"668a480a-3498-4c09-9de4-644f261bab97","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":152,"end":153,"value":"0817adc9-541e-41f6-bc16-5dd3b78a6404","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f2570cd1-36ce-48f8-92fe-0b50d86c1dab","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":231,"end":234,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"66814ac0-652b-4640-a0d3-e499ecaa799d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":237,"end":237,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3780be87-86fe-4738-a921-fe75fd3c52db","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":245,"end":248,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"13990fd0-bd1c-4c71-bfc1-702a62699ce1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":254,"end":255,"value":"0817adc9-541e-41f6-bc16-5dd3b78a6404","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3fbf095a-c23a-41ac-bc97-90a0a3369df1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":258,"end":258,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"e1bbd75f-3208-43e9-b68b-b87c840f88bc","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c4b6f578-aea0-40fc-a2f8-1b59d6bdc048","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"As to the proposed alliance with the Nasi, thou writest saying that thou hast not yet had a reply from Andrea Quaratesi. I do not think much reliance is to be placed on him in this sort of affair, and the time that is passing away with so much waiting will not return. It seems to me there ought to be a girl somewhere of noble birth, good education and irreproachable character, but in very poor circumstances: if such were to be found it would be very much to our purpose, as it would ensure thy living in peace. For\u00A0the love of God, take her without a dowry. I think\u00A0thou couldst find something of the kind in Florence, and it would give me the liveliest satisfaction, for thou wouldst be free from the fear of frivolity and extravagance, and wouldst be a benefactor to someone else, as others have been to thee. But thou art become a rich man without knowing how. I do not wish to tell thee the miserable state in which I found our family when I began to work for it first: a whole volume would not suffice for my story, and I never received any return save ingratitude. Ask God, therefore, to put it into thy heart to realise what thy position is, and go not in search of pomps and\u00A0empty vanities.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"eb36b0e8-bdf1-405a-a2ea-44f151806176","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":37,"end":40,"value":"55950ce5-7d69-47b9-b543-46b1813bad35","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5e395539-5674-40db-8ae6-a1d16a96cc2d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":43,"end":46,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"35f56760-13f9-47da-85f7-0596eaf25c20","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":68,"end":71,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4d97c183-2f3d-4092-a1e7-494792101da2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":103,"end":118,"value":"ee634ee7-0cda-4976-a002-eaa7c6548782","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1e348672-cbce-45bb-bbb7-bade93404d72","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":121,"end":121,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7492fddd-3527-4668-87e7-d9d08aa13b55","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":169,"end":171,"value":"ee634ee7-0cda-4976-a002-eaa7c6548782","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c33761cd-1191-4259-9398-b3b31c95be57","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":281,"end":282,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"27ac0276-4a7f-484b-a1ad-77cea9934e12","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":304,"end":307,"value":"85764433-0e1c-44ab-9822-e6c389b39ef7","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9141770